            <p class="italic relative text-headings_second text-xl xs:text-base">Hiring a lawyer can sometimes be overwhelming. Having someone who genuinely cares about you is hard to come by these days but Kenny Habetz is one of the only lawyers I completely trust. He constantly demonstrates high standards and character rarely seen in business today. He is extremely intelligent, passionate, hardworking and will get the job done.</p>
